      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a name=\"BKMK_HybridOfferings\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Choose between Intune standalone and Intune with Configuration Manager"
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        4186,
        4270
      ],
      "content": "You might choose <ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[wit_nextref](../Token/wit_nextref_md.md)]</ph> stand-alone if:"
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        4271,
        4367
      ],
      "content": "You might choose <ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[wit_nextref](../Token/wit_nextref_md.md)]</ph> + Configuration Manager if:"
