        5451
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "-   You have more than 50,000 devices to manage.",
      "pos": [
        5457,
        5505
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "-   You have on-premises IT infrastructure in place, or plan to deploy such infrastructure.",
      "pos": [
        5511,
        5602
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this configuration, the device and resource management experience is fully unified.",
      "pos": [
        5603,
        5689
      ]
    },
    {
